text.tspan: Global meat demand if everyone ate like the average citizen of..., 1961 to 2021
Hypothetical global meat demand if everyone in the world ate the same quantity as the average citizen of a given
country. For example, data for the US in 2020 shows global meat demand if everyone in the world consumed the same
amount of meat as the average US citizen in 2020. The curve for "World" gives the actual global meat production in
Data source: Our World in Data based on the Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations
